{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This repository contains my public scripts for Reaper. I hope they will be useful to people.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Installation instructions:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Open Reaper (!).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Go to Extensions -> ReaPack -> Manage repositories...\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Click on Import/export -> Import repositories...\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Copy the following URL into the text field: https://github.com/poulhoi/phoi_ReaScripts/raw/master/index.xml\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Hit 'OK'.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Tested only on MacOS Mojave for now, but everything should work on Windows and possibly Linux as well. Feel free to reach out to me on the Reaper forums if you have questions or problems: https://forum.cockos.com/member.php?u=140016\par}
